title: What font is this?
content:
Hello,

Does anyone know the fonts used here. I have 'The First' as Commerce Gothic, but am struggling with the rest. Any help greatly appreciated.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20100201065342im_/http:/typophile.com/files/418U5EcfAsL_6040._SS500_.jpg)
author: exetercity

comments.content:
Well, TYCOON and VANDERBILT are Grand Canyon Tourist from Red Rooster:

( [http://new.myfonts.com/fonts/redrooster/grand-canyon-rr/tourist/](http://web.archive.org/web/20100201065342/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/redrooster/grand-canyon-rr/tourist/ "http://new.myfonts.com/fonts/redrooster/grand-canyon-rr/tourist/"))
Great. Thanks so much for your help!
The script looks very similar to Palace Script, not right but kinda close.
